{"id":383914,"date":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":22}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"124","ytitle":"","mtitle":"小木瓜学耕地","ftitle":"","authors":["索玉润"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"索玉润"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六岁小木瓜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是个好娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸妈妈下地去干活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他跪在地板上来回爬:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小猫当做老黄牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竹凳当做双铧犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步学耕地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右手拿条赶牛鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左手扶着双铧犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛走十步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木瓜爬一步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惹得奶奶笑嘟嘟:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“等你这娃娃会使犁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛早换上拖拉机。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入4号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1959\\01\\591m031401.JPG\">"}]}